Program: Outlook
Title: Smallest Car in the World
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr8f
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The 'smallest car in the world', which packs up into a suitcase and weighs 20 kilograms. Also, which country has the happiest teenagers?, the origins and legacy of the myth of El Dorado and, the decaying glamour of Baghdad.